{
    "name": "Librarian",
    "type": "npc",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Librarian",
            "type": "section",
            "text": "Keepers of knowledge, librarians document discoveries, events, and laws. The best librarians record events twice; once for public record, and again to record how events truly unfolded. A librarian typically knows four to six additional languages, often including <a aonid=\"4\" game-obj=\"Languages\">Elven</a> and <a aonid=\"2\" game-obj=\"Languages\">Draconic</a>. A librarian is a 3rd-level challenge for encounters involving research.<br/><br/><b><u><a aonid=\"5\" game-obj=\"Skills\" general=\"true\">Recall Knowledge - Humanoid</a></u> (<u><a aonid=\"14\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Society</a></u>)</b>: DC 13",
            "sources": [
                {
                    "type": "source",
                    "name": "Gamemastery Guide",
                    "link": {
                        "type": "link",
                        "name": "Gamemastery Guide pg. 240",
                        "alt": "Gamemastery Guide pg. 240",
                        "href": "https://paizo.com/products/btq01zq7"
                    },
                    "page": 240
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "name": "Scholars",
            "type": "section",
            "sections": [
                {
